&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with other team leads to synchronize development processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and produce code and technical design documents of peers to ensure high standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and enforce coding standards and guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate competence in navigating the organization to connect with relevant individuals and resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
